# 8. RECURSIVE GOVERNANCE FRAMEWORK

The defining characteristic of the CORE is recursion.

Rather than making a decision once:

The CORE continuously re-evaluates decisions.

---

## Governance Loop

```
Collect Data
      ↓
Analyze State
      ↓
Generate Decisions
      ↓
Execute Actions
      ↓
Observe Results
      ↓
Update Governance Model
      ↓
Repeat
```

This creates a self-correcting architecture.

